title: Fence
content:
Fence may refer to:

Construction[edit | edit source]

  • Fencing, a hotspot in the Formal Garden of a player-owned house
    • Garden fence, a Formal Garden fencing
    • Picket fence, a Formal Garden fencing
    • Wooden fence, a Formal Garden fencing
    • Fence (Construction), the fences that can be constructed in a player-owned house formal garden
  • Fence space, a hotspot in the Superior Garden of a player-owned house
    • Redwood fence, a Superior Garden fencing
    • Obsidian fence, a Superior Garden fencing

Agility shortcut[edit | edit source]

  • The Fence south of Varrock, requiring 13 Agility to use
  • The Broken Fence on the east side of Rellekka, requiring 57 Agility, providing access into and out of the city
  • The Low Fence in western Burgh de Rott, requiring 25 Agility, providing quick access to the fairy ring code BIP and the Abandoned Mine

Scenery[edit | edit source]

  • Fence end, two ends of fence that can be seen over the west wall of Darkmeyer near the entrance to Barrows
